@startuml Tool-Invocation-Flow
!theme plain

title 工具调用时序图 - Tool Invocation Sequence

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceStyle arrow
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #F3E5F5
skinparam noteBorderColor #7B1FA2

' === Participants ===
participant OperatorAgent as "OperatorAgent\n(Python)"
participant ToolManager as "ToolManager"
participant ToolRegistry as "ToolRegistry\n(Singleton)"
participant JavaServiceTool as "JavaMicroserviceTool"
participant HTTPClient as "httpx\nAsyncClient"
participant JavaService as "Java Service\n(Spring Boot)"
participant MySQL as "MySQL\nDatabase"

' === Auto-number ===
autonumber 1.1

' === Main Flow ===
group 工具调用流程
    OperatorAgent -> OperatorAgent : 执行任务\n需要获取数据
    OperatorAgent -> ToolManager : invoke_tool(tool_name, input)
    activate ToolManager

    ToolManager -> ToolRegistry : get_tool(tool_name)
    activate ToolRegistry
    ToolRegistry --> ToolManager : Tool instance
    deactivate ToolRegistry

    ToolManager -> JavaServiceTool : tool.run(input)
    activate JavaServiceTool

    JavaServiceTool -> JavaServiceTool : 构造请求参数
    JavaServiceTool -> HTTPClient : async client.post(url, json)
    activate HTTPClient

    HTTPClient -> JavaService : HTTP POST /api/v1/query/operators
    activate JavaService

    JavaService -> JavaService : 处理请求\n参数验证
    JavaService -> MySQL : JDBC Query
    activate MySQL
    MySQL --> JavaService : ResultSet
    deactivate MySQL

    JavaService --> HTTPClient : JSON Response
    deactivate JavaService

    HTTPClient --> JavaServiceTool : HTTP Response
    deactivate HTTPClient

    JavaServiceTool -> JavaServiceTool : 解析响应\n构造 ToolResult
    JavaServiceTool --> ToolManager : ToolResult
    deactivate JavaServiceTool

    ToolManager --> OperatorAgent : ToolResult
    deactivate ToolManager
end group

' === Error Handling ===
note over JavaServiceTool #FFF3E0
  **错误处理:**
  - 连接超时: 重试 3 次
  - 服务不可用: 返回错误信息
  - 参数错误: 返回验证错误
end note

' === Semaphore Control ===
note over ToolManager #E8F5E9
  **并发控制:**
  Semaphore(10) 限制并发数
  防止资源耗尽
end note

@enduml